item.description:
This is the big one. This Tuesday, voters in two dozen states will
determine whether 2009 ushers in a new era of limited government and
peace, or whether one of two brands of tyranny will engulf this country,
ushering in a new era of terror, poverty and death.

We stand at the edge of the abyss, and on Tuesday, those people will
push us over, or pull us back.

One thing is for certain: on Tuesday, we are going to eat, drink and be
merry, and you are welcome to join us. Come for dinner anytime after 5
pm, socialize with your fellow freedom lovers, watch the results come
in on the huge projection TV, and stay for as long as you care to (or
until Nanny State says you have to go home).
item.name: Super Taproom Tuesday
